  "helpTitle": "Help & FAQ",
  "helpHeaderTitle": "How can we\nhelp you?",
  "helpHeaderSubtitle": "Find answers to your questions or contact our support.",
  "helpFaqSectionTitle": "Frequently asked questions",
  "helpNeedHelp": "Need help?",
  "helpFaqQ1": "How do I place an order?",
  "helpFaqA1": "Browse restaurants from the home screen, choose your dishes, add them to your cart and confirm your order. You can track your delivery in real time.",
  "helpFaqQ2": "What are the delivery times?",
  "helpFaqA2": "Delivery takes on average 30 to 45 minutes depending on distance and restaurant preparation time. You can track your order in real time from the Orders tab.",
  "helpFaqQ3": "How do I cancel an order?",
  "helpFaqA3": "You can cancel your order from the Orders tab as long as it hasn't been accepted by the restaurant. Go to the order details and tap \"Cancel\".",
  "helpFaqQ4": "What payment methods do you accept?",
  "helpFaqA4": "Amara accepts Mobile Money (Orange Money, MTN Money, Wave), credit cards (Visa, Mastercard) and cash on delivery.",
  "helpFaqQ5": "How do I add a delivery address?",
  "helpFaqA5": "Go to your Profile > My addresses, then tap \"Add\". You can save multiple addresses and set a default address.",
  "helpFaqQ6": "My order hasn't arrived, what should I do?",
  "helpFaqA6": "Contact our support via the chat at the bottom of this page or call us. We will do our best to resolve your issue quickly.",
  "helpFaqQ7": "How can I become a partner restaurant?",
  "helpFaqA7": "Send us an email at partners@amara.app with your restaurant name, location and menu. Our team will get back to you within 48 hours.",
  "helpContactChat": "Live chat",
  "helpContactChatSubtitle": "Response in a few minutes",
  "helpContactChatSoon": "Chat coming soon",
  "helpContactEmail": "Email",
  "helpContactEmailAddress": "support@amara.app",
